column5: Just wondering if anyone has a report from Witch bay on LOTW. Headed To Witch Bay camp in a couple of days, but it has been about five years since we have fished that area. Any location, depth, or colors hottest for walleye? or musky? Thanks Icedog
I've been to Witch Bay Camp. ( 1964 I believe ).......lol Oh, how I'd love to see that area once more eh!!!!!!!!!! Perhaps some day soon. Good luck & tight lines!!!!

I just got back from there 2 weeks ago, fished bottom bouncers in 23-25'. Blue Colorado blades worked the best for us. They were not running to big but we did manage to get a lot of walleyes over 20 with the biggest being 28 for the week. Dog
Hey guys thanks for the responses. Icedog
